                            <comment id="12788797" author="cos" created="Thu, 10 Dec 2009 17:23:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That should do it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What have you been running to get to this problem? This is a side effect of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6386&quot; title=&quot;NameNode&amp;#39;s HttpServer can&amp;#39;t instantiate InetSocketAddress: IllegalArgumentException is thrown&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-6386&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HDFS-771&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and is extremely hard to reproduce.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
